<subSubSection lastPageId="13" lastPageNumber="76" pageId="12" pageNumber="75" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,679,775]" pageId="12" pageNumber="75">
<emphasis box="[151,273,679,704]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="75" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,266,679,704]" pageId="12" pageNumber="75">Diagnosis</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Black, shiny, finely grey pruinescent; legs dark yellow; scape and pedicel yellow; wing hyaline, veins yellow, pterostigma inconspicuous, light yellow; peniform setae on fore femur, fore tibia, fore tarsomeres 1 and 2, hind tarsomere 1 and lateral margins of abdominal tergites.
</paragraph>
