<figureCitation box="[737,821,1162,1186]" captionStart="FIGURES 60–69" captionStartId="12.[151,264,1670,1693]" captionTargetBox="[272,1326,835,1649]" captionTargetId="figure-382@12.[251,1336,829,1649]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 60–69. Empis penniventris Bezzi, holotype ♀. 60, head, lateral view; 61, frons, frontal view; 62; thorax, dorsal view; 63, right foreleg, anterior view; 64, right midleg, posterior view; 65, right hindleg, anterior view; 66, abdomen, lateral view; 67, terminalia, lateral view; 68, terminalia, dorsal segments, dorsal view; 69, terminalia, ventral segments, ventral view. Scales: Figures 60, 63–65 = 1.0 mm; 61–62, 66 = 0.5 mm; 67–69 = 0.2 mm." pageId="13" pageNumber="76">Fig. 67</figureCitation>
), slightly more sclerotized laterally, slightly acuminate distally (
<figureCitation box="[249,333,1199,1223]" captionStart="FIGURES 60–69" captionStartId="12.[151,264,1670,1693]" captionTargetBox="[272,1326,835,1649]" captionTargetId="figure-382@12.[251,1336,829,1649]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 60–69. Empis penniventris Bezzi, holotype ♀. 60, head, lateral view; 61, frons, frontal view; 62; thorax, dorsal view; 63, right foreleg, anterior view; 64, right midleg, posterior view; 65, right hindleg, anterior view; 66, abdomen, lateral view; 67, terminalia, lateral view; 68, terminalia, dorsal segments, dorsal view; 69, terminalia, ventral segments, ventral view. Scales: Figures 60, 63–65 = 1.0 mm; 61–62, 66 = 0.5 mm; 67–69 = 0.2 mm." pageId="13" pageNumber="76">Fig. 69</figureCitation>
); sternite 10 longer than tergite 10; cercus broken (
<figureCitation box="[903,988,1199,1223]" captionStart="FIGURES 60–69" captionStartId="12.[151,264,1670,1693]" captionTargetBox="[272,1326,835,1649]" captionTargetId="figure-382@12.[251,1336,829,1649]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 60–69. Empis penniventris Bezzi, holotype ♀. 60, head, lateral view; 61, frons, frontal view; 62; thorax, dorsal view; 63, right foreleg, anterior view; 64, right midleg, posterior view; 65, right hindleg, anterior view; 66, abdomen, lateral view; 67, terminalia, lateral view; 68, terminalia, dorsal segments, dorsal view; 69, terminalia, ventral segments, ventral view. Scales: Figures 60, 63–65 = 1.0 mm; 61–62, 66 = 0.5 mm; 67–69 = 0.2 mm." pageId="13" pageNumber="76">Fig. 68</figureCitation>
